instructions = "The flag is right next to you, but the direct path is blocked!

This level tests your spatial reasoning. To reach the goal, you will need to guide the robot through a narrow corridor by planning several steps ahead.

Think carefully about which direction the robot will face after each turn before you command it to move!"
